# ===========================================
# 錯誤測試
# ===========================================

### 測試缺少 name
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "description": "這是描述"
}

### 測試 name 為空字串
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "這是描述"
}

### 測試 name 超過 20 字元
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "這是一個超過二十個字元的分類名稱測試"
}

### 測試重複的分類名稱（需先建立「小說」分類）
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "小說",
  "description": "重複的分類"
}

### 測試沒有 Token（應該回傳 401）
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試分類"
}

### 測試使用 User Token（應該回傳 403）
# 請替換為 User 的 Token
@userToken = YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "name": "測試分類"
}

